{"tid":1673282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔connect加泰，都可以講句「多謝」","createTime":"2019-10-24T14:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T16:38:32.000Z","uid":312358,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"33bcad032bdae4460b6402f36a3f15cfb022dbe4","tid":1673282,"uid":312358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T14:31:37.000Z","msg":"話我左膠都係咁講<br />\n明白好多手足想過人權法而唔connect加泰<br />\n唔connect唔緊要<br />\n但唔好開口埋口「加泰狗」<br />\n人哋肯喺集會改編改詞唱我哋嘅歌<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">仲唱得好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n淨係份誠意都感動啦<br />\n<br />\n中美咩關係大家都知啦 依個亦係美國撐我哋贏嘅原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相信美國係明白事理<br />\n我哋都成日叫人Stand with HK<br />\n當人哋支持我哋時 我哋講返句「多謝」都唔過份<br />\n所以手足們如果認同<br />\n<strong>一齊去reddit個post多謝加泰嘅心意好唔好？</strong><br />\n<br />\n加泰人喺加泰唱加泰version願榮光歸香港<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1673144\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1673144</a><br />\n<br />\n預咗個post會好多負皮<br />\n重申：你可以唔connect 一句「多謝」已經夠<br />\n最後 希望大家都可以唱得咁好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3327b882b4b64a23fcf1bfb420d6b9b62c495fa5","tid":1673282,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T14:32:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/guewjRY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FguewjRY.jpg&h=ac95176a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"79c6599e925179ecfd2817b73f73cf51ed32aa05","tid":1673282,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T14:32:53.000Z","msg":"多謝加泰手足<br />\n<br />\n早幾日吹完反加泰集會風，今晚就開始吹恥笑早幾日反加泰集會嘅風<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1673275\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1673275</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"028a2616dd8fab74c9078e921eda115de4446c87","tid":1673282,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:00:1